{"tid":2209312,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"[ww3？] 解放軍戰神轟炸機「轟-6K」轟炸美軍關島基地","createTime":"2020-09-19T14:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T14:58:51.000Z","uid":210755,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b4fd1c7e41025894cda6a3ae6795cb18a45da8f2","tid":2209312,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:21:35.000Z","msg":"真係開戰？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點算好 好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美角力｜轟-6K模擬炸關島基地影片曝光 解放軍擺明車馬挑釁美國<br />\n中美「冷戰2.0」，雙方劍拔弩張，越來越多迹象顯示正演變成一場熱戰。解放軍空軍今日在官方微博發放了一段最新短片，當中出現被內媒吹噓為「戰神」的戰略轟炸機「轟-6K」模擬轟炸美軍關島基地畫面，有關訊息極具挑釁性，因而引起了外界的高度關注。<span class=\"red\">據悉，這也是解放軍首次擺明車馬、公開針對美軍基地的相關畫面。</span><br />\n解放軍空軍官微「空軍在線」今日發放的短片，以真實片段配合模擬的3D動畫，視覺上營造出轟-6K進行攻擊任務的全過程。影片一開始便播放轟-6K在空軍基地中進行起飛前準備的片段，接着起飛後接近指定目標，駕駛員鎖定目標，發射導彈對一處基地進行炸轟，命中後冒起巨大火球及濃煙。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">被「轟炸」的疑似美軍關島基地，冒出如同核爆的火球。<br />\n</span><br />\n上月24日，中國各大軍媒曾密集宣傳，解放軍中部戰區空軍航空兵所屬的「第一支」戰略轟炸機部隊，當時出鏡的就是轟-6K。<br />\n轟-6K是轟-6的深度改進型號，從早期的中型轟炸機被升級為如今的戰略轟炸機。轟-6K首次在2007年曝光，機身獲重新設計，機頭安裝大型雷達，駕駛艙實現「玻璃座艙化」，更新電子設備，配置彈射逃生系統，改用俄製D30-KP-2引擎，機翼下共有6個掛點。<br />\n<br />\n轟-6K的主要機載武器包括空地導彈和巡航導彈，作戰半徑超過3,500公里。而轟-6K近日不斷出現在台灣海峽、南海、西太平洋上空，成為中國進行戰略威懾的最強轟炸機。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200919/YB2RNKDJN5C23IXYU4TWW6ATAY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200919%2FYB2RNKDJN5C23IXYU4TWW6ATAY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxEzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=dfbcf752\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200919%2FYB2RNKDJN5C23IXYU4TWW6ATAY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=321fb791\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200919/YB2RNKDJN5C23IXYU4TWW6ATAY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"c2339a2bce15fbc0f7f797783ee162418d71a98c","tid":2209312,"uid":39182,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />偷襲珍珠港2.0"},{"pid":"fd74bb1a2e27a4a25e0410908fde87ebd86ef715","tid":2209312,"uid":25525,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"呢d野諗都已經犯大忌仲要拍埋出嚟，真弱智"},{"pid":"fa5ce83052012e01033d4b192c4f43684faea33d","tid":2209312,"uid":19528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"Twitter 見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不斷提供彈藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23a5650c768e995b407fce20d2a6564ec2a9b79","tid":2209312,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd74bb1a2e27a4a25e0410908fde87ebd86ef715","tid":2209312,"uid":25525,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"呢d野諗都已經犯大忌仲要拍埋出嚟，真弱智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"美帝亡我之心不死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能真係震懾到美帝呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb20d5269d4920002dd1e7b93f351f5e99e6a849","tid":2209312,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2339a2bce15fbc0f7f797783ee162418d71a98c","tid":2209312,"uid":39182,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\